<!-- components/brainwave-realtime/brainwave-realtime.wxml -->
<!-- 实时脑波可视化组件 -->
<view class="brainwave-realtime-container {{brainwaveType}} {{isPlaying ? 'playing' : 'paused'}}">
  <canvas 
    id="brainwave-canvas" 
    type="2d" 
    class="brainwave-canvas"
    bindtap="onCanvasTap"
  ></canvas>
  
  <!-- 脑波信息显示 -->
  <view class="brainwave-info">
    <view class="brainwave-name">{{brainwaveConfig[brainwaveType].name}}</view>
    <view class="brainwave-freq">{{brainwaveConfig[brainwaveType].baseFreq}}Hz</view>
  </view>
  
  <!-- 状态指示器 -->
  <view class="status-indicator {{isPlaying ? 'active' : 'inactive'}}">
    <view class="status-dot"></view>
    <text class="status-text">{{isPlaying ? '实时分析' : '静态模式'}}</text>
  </view>
</view>
